gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 115, Jazz 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Jazz, 115-113. Paolo Banchero led the way for the Magic with 30 points (9-13 FG), nine rebounds and five assists for the Magic, while Franz Wagner added 21 points, four rebounds and five assists in the victory. Lauri Markkanen tallied 22 points and seven rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 3-2 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 2-4.
